Curses::Widgets Module for Perl
==============================

Author: Arthur Corliss
Date:  January 12, 1999

Description:
------------

High level access to basic Curses widgets and related functions.

Instructions:
-------------

Hopefully, all that one needs to do is:

	perl Makefile.pl
	make install

If this is not the case, feel free to send a flame to
corliss@odinicfoundation.org, and I'll get on it.  :-)
